# ЁЯЪл ржзрж╛ржк рззрзж: Role-based Protect ржХрж░рж╛

### Controller-level:

```csharp
[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
public class DashboardController : Controller
{
}
```

### Action-level:

```csharp
[Authorize(Roles = "User")]
public IActionResult Profile() => View();
```

